snippet.title: Jump King Console Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Jump King is launching today on Nintendo Switch Playstation 4 and Xbox One!
It is time for console gamers to take up the challenge! Do you really think you are ready?

About Jump King:
Take up the challenge and face true high-stakes platforming in Jump King! Struggle upwards in search of the Smoking Hot Babe of legend, but explore with care; a single missed jump could lead to a long fall back down…

Jump King is also available on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1061090/Jump_King/

Follow Nexile on twitter at @nexilegames → https://twitter.com/nexilegames
Follow Ukiyo on twitter at @UkiyoPublishing → https://twitter.com/UkiyoPublishing
